description: With a mission to make the Houston food truck scene a bit more interesting, two talented chefs offer the only selection of wild game in town. A few of the untame-ly tasty items you’ll find at this truck include elk, bison, wild boar, duck wings, and Bull Shark Scottish Ale battered crab sandwiches (to name a few). For all this and more, come unleash your appetite at Predator & Prey Grill!
name: Predator & Prey Grill
